<h1>Luna – Demo Health & Fitness App</h1>

<h2>About Luna</h2>
<p>
Luna is a demo health and fitness application created for educational and demonstration purposes.
It provides period tracking features, health-related articles, and real-time interaction modules
to showcase mobile application development concepts.
</p>

<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>
Luna respects user privacy. This application does not sell, rent, or share user data with third
parties for commercial purposes.
</p>

<h2>Data Usage</h2>
<p>
The app may store user-entered data locally on the device or securely in the backend only to
support application functionality. No sensitive personal data is collected for advertising,
analytics, or monetization purposes.
</p>

<h2>Medical Disclaimer</h2>
<p>
Luna is a demo project and is not intended for medical diagnosis, treatment, or professional
health advice. Users should consult qualified healthcare professionals for medical concerns.
</p>

<h2>Support & Contact</h2>
<p>
If you have any questions, feedback, or support requests regarding this demo application,
you can contact the developer at:
</p>
